    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 39.7433333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "ムカつく！\nムカつく、ムカつく、ムカつくっ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so pissed!\nPissed‚ pissed‚ pissed!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.7433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 40.65
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 41.45
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 43.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "kana、うるさいわよ\n子供じゃないんだから、大人しくして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kana‚ be quiet.\nYou're not a child‚ so behave yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 47.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "納得出来ないの！　kana達はBIG4なんだよ？\nなのに、こんなみっともないライブバトルになるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't accept this! Kana and the others are BIG4‚ right?\nHow could we have such a pathetic live battle?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 57.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "でもこれは、紛れもない現実よ\n月スト相手に、こんな結果になってしまった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But this is the undeniable reality.\nWe ended up with this result against Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.81,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "相手は、私達が思っていた以上に強かった\nこの数週間で、飛躍的に実力を高めていた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our opponent was stronger than we thought.\nThey dramatically improved their skills in these past few weeks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 72.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "相手の力量ぐらい、素直に認めなさい\n私達はプロなんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just admit the opponent's strength.\nWe're professionals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.2433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 78.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "よく言うよ\n二人だって月ストのこと、思いっきり舐めてたくせに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're one to talk.\nYou two were totally looking down on Moon Tempest too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 85.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "舐めてはいないわ。あらゆるデータを元に\n自分達より格は下だと思っていただけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We weren't looking down on them. Based on all the data‚\nwe just thought they were a lower rank than us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "油断も手加減もしたつもりは一切ない\nスリクスは全力で挑んだ……kanaだってそうよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't intend to let my guard down or hold back at all.\nⅢX went in with our full strength… Kana‚ you too‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 100.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "当然。格下相手でも、全力で潰すっていうのが\nkana達が唯一共有している絶対のスタンスでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. Even against someone inferior‚ crushing them with all our might is\nthe absolute stance we share‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 109
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "そう。そしてその結果……\n私達は、月ストに勝った",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. And as a result…\nwe beat Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 114.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 114.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "結果は出したわ。何がそんなに不満なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We got the result. What are you so dissatisfied with?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 117.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 121.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "月スト相手に接戦だったことが不満なの！\nkanaはね、完・全・勝・利！　以外に興味ないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm dissatisfied that it was a close call against Moon Tempest!\nKana is only interested in a… complete… victory!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 127.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "面倒な性格ね、まったく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What a troublesome personality…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "あんたに言われたくないし！　ていうかあんたも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want to hear that from you! And besides‚ you too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 135.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "……正直、接戦を強いられたからこそ\n私達もいつも以上に、力を発揮することが出来た",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Honestly‚ because we were forced into a close call‚\nwe were able to exert even more power than usual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "結果的に、これまでよりも\nかなりレベルの高いステージにはなったわね",
      "translations": {
